Master an ever-growing roster of diverse Legends, deep tactical squad play and bold new innovations that go beyond the Battle Royale experience—all within a rugged world where anything goes. Welcome to the next evolution of Hero Shooter.', 'https://www.igdb.com/games/apex-legends', '["Xbox Series X|S", "PlayStation 4", "Nintendo Switch 2", "PC (Microsoft Windows)", "PlayStation 5", "Xbox One", "Nintendo Switch"]', NULL, NULL, 0, 1.0, '2026-07-20 04:02:06', '2026-07-20 04:02:06');
